name: A Jedi's Plans
Lore: 'The guidance of experienced Jedi allowed Luke to confront Vader.',
Text: 'Deploy on a site.  Nightfall is canceled.  While you have 8 or fewer cards in hand, non-unique characters (except clones), vehicles, starships, weapons, and devices are immune to Monnok.  Once per turn, may use 2 Force to deploy Jedi Archives or a battleground planet location (except sector) not on table from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. (Immune to Alter.)',
